        "body": "Hi [~ywskycn], how is the issue going? I want to take it over.\nAutomatic failover has been already supported, however, when executing graceful failover from command line, UnsupportedOperationException is thrown.\n{code:title=RMHAServiceTarget.java}\n  @Override\n  public InetSocketAddress getZKFCAddress() {\n    // TODO (YARN-1177): ZKFC implementation\n    throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"RMHAServiceTarget doesn't have \" +\n        \"a corresponding ZKFC address\");\n  }\n{code}",
